<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>网站设置 - 卡密接码平台</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/admin.css">
  <style>
    .settings-page-header { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; justify-content:space-between; gap:18px; margin-bottom:18px; }
    .settings-page-header h2 { margin:0 0 6px; }
    .settings-page-header p { margin:0; max-width:590px; color:#6e6e73; font-size:13px; line-height:1.55; }
    .settings-card { max-width:820px; }
    .settings-card-head { display:flex; align-items:flex-start; gap:12px; padding-bottom:16px; margin-bottom:18px; border-bottom:1px solid #ececf0; }
    .settings-card-icon { flex:0 0 auto; display:grid; width:36px; height:36px; place-items:center; border-radius:9px; background:#eff7f2; color:#218452; font-size:17px; }
    .settings-card-head h3 { margin:0 0 4px; color:#1d1d1f; }
    .settings-card-head p { margin:0; color:#6e6e73; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5; }
    .site-settings-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap:14px; }
    .site-settings-grid .form-group { margin:0; }
    .site-settings-grid input { max-width:none; min-height:40px; box-sizing:border-box; }
    .settings-hint { margin:16px 0 18px; padding:11px 12px; border:1px solid #e1ece4; border-radius:7px; background:#f7fbf8; color:#52705d; font-size:12px; line-height:1.55; }
    .settings-actions { display:flex; justify-content:flex-end; gap:10px; border-top:1px solid #ececf0; padding-top:16px; }
    .settings-actions .btn { min-height:38px; }
    @media (max-width:760px) {
      .settings-page-header { display:block; }
      .settings-card { max-width:none; }
      .site-settings-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:12px; }
      .settings-actions { justify-content:stretch; }
      .settings-actions .btn { width:100%; text-align:center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { admin, active: 'settings' }) %>
  <main class="main">
    <div class="settings-page-header">
      <div>
        <h2>网站设置</h2>
        <p>管理全站显示与号码领取规则。API 平台的账号、Token 和接口地址请在“API 对接”中单独维护。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% if (success) { %><div class="message message-success"><%= success %></div><% } %>
    <% if (error) { %><div class="message message-error"><%= error %></div><% } %>

    <section class="card settings-card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="settings-card-head">
          <div class="settings-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">&#9881;</div>
          <div>
            <h3>基础运行规则</h3>
            <p>这些设置会立即应用到用户端的号码展示、冷却限制和未收码号码的自动释放流程。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <form method="POST" action="/admin/settings">
          <div class="site-settings-grid">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="siteName">网站名称</label>
              <input id="siteName" name="site_name" value="<%= siteName %>" maxlength="40" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="releaseTimeout">号码自动释放时间（分钟）</label>
              <input id="releaseTimeout" name="release_timeout" value="<%= releaseTimeout %>" type="number" min="1" max="60" step="1" required>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="cooldownSeconds">获取新号码冷却时间（秒）</label>
              <input id="cooldownSeconds" name="cooldown_seconds" value="<%= cooldownSeconds %>" type="number" min="10" max="3600" step="1" required>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="settings-hint">自动释放只会处理尚未收到验证码的号码；已经收到验证码的卡密记录不会因为这个规则被提前清除。</p>
          <div class="settings-actions"><button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">保存网站设置</button></div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
